      <odd id="aspace_2e6f537bf088e8da92fa6a8903a5959a">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 14-B (YRG 14-B), Records of academic departments and programs of the Yale Faculty of Arts and Sciences.</p>  
      </odd>
